obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (47558)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855&sectionId=47558&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Jammu and Kashmir (Extension`
  line `of Laws) Act, 1956.`
  line
  line `(2) It shall come into force on such date^1`
  line `as the Central Government may, by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, appoint.`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. 1st November, 1956, vide notification No. S. R. O. 2327, dated 10th October, 1956, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary,`
  line `Part II, sec. 3.`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (47559)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Extension and amendment of certain laws.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855&sectionId=47559&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Acts and Ordinance mentioned in the`
  line `Schedule and all rules, orders and regulations made there under are hereby extended to, and shall be in`
  line `force, in the State of Jammu and Kashmir*.`
  line
  line `(2) With effect from the commencement of this Acts the Act and Ordinance mentioned in the`
  line `Schedule shall be amended as specified therein.`
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (47560)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Construction of references to laws not in force in Jammu and Kashmir.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855&sectionId=47560&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `Any reference in any`
  line `Act or in the Ordinance mentioned in the Schedule to a law which is not in force in the State of Jammu`
  line `and Kashmir* shall, in relation to that State, be construed as a reference to the corresponding law, if any, in`
  line `force in that State.`
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (47561)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Construction of references to authorities where new authorities have been constituted.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855&sectionId=47561&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line Any
  line `reference by whatever form of words in any law for the time being in force in the State of Jammu and`
  line `Kashmir* to any authority competent at the date of the passing of that law to exercise any powers or`
  line `discharge any functions in that State shall, where a corresponding new authority has been constituted by`
  line `or under any law now extended to that State, have effect as if it were a reference to the new authority.`
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (47562)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Repeals and savings.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855&sectionId=47562&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `If immediately before the commencement of this Act there is in force in`
  line `the State of Jammu and Kashmir* any law corresponding to any Act or Ordinance now extended to that`
  line `State, that law shall, save as otherwise expressly provided in this Act, stand repealed on such`
  line `commencement:`
  line
  line `Provided that the repeal shall not affect`
  line
  line `(a) the previous operation of any law so repealed or anything duly done or suffered hereunder,`
  line
  line `(b) any right, privilege, obligation or liability acquired, accrued or incurred under any law so`
  line repealed,
  line
  line `(c) any penalty, forfeiture or punishment incurred in respect of any offence committed against`
  line `any law so repealed, or`
  line
  line `(d) any investigation, legal proceeding or remedy in respect of any such right, privilege`
  line `obligation, liability, penalty, forfeiture or punishment as aforesaid;`
  line
  line `and any such investigation, legal proceeding or remedy may be instituted, continued or enforced, and any`
  line `such penalty, forfeiture or punishment may be imposed, as if this Act had not been passed:`
  line
  line `Provided further that, subject to the preceding proviso, anything done or any action taken (including`
  line `any appointment or delegation made, notification, instruction or direction issued, form, bye-law or`
  line `scheme framed, certificate obtained, permit or licence granted or registration effected) under any such law`
  line `shall be deemed to have been done or taken under the corresponding provisions of the Act or Ordinance`
  line `now extended to that State, and shall continue to be in force accordingly unless and until superseded by`
  line `anything done or any action taken under the said Act or Ordinance.`
obj_root_law_sections_6:
  sectionId (47563)
  sectionNo (6)
  orderNo 6
  title `Power to remove difficulties.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_6_content
  footnotes `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855&sectionId=47563&sectionno=6&orderno=6&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_34_00003_195662_1517807324855
obj_root_law_sections_6_content:
  string
  line `(1) If any difficulty arises in giving effect to the provisions of any`
  line `Act or Ordinance now extended to the State of Jammu and Kashmir*, the Central Government may, by`
  line `order notified in the Official Gazette, make such provisions or give such directions as appear to it`
  line `necessary for the removal of the difficulty.`
  line
  line `(2) In particular, and without prejudice to the generality of the foregoing power, any such notified`
  line `order may,`
  line
  line `(a) specify the corresponding authorities within the meaning of section 4,`
  line
  line `(b) provide for the transfer of any matter pending immediately before the commencement of this`
  line `Act before any court, tribunal or other authority, to any corresponding court, tribunal or authority for`
  line disposal,
  line
  line `(c) specify the areas or circumstances in which, or the extent to which, or the conditions subject`
  line `to which, anything done or any action taken (including any of the matters specified in the second`
  line `proviso to section 5) under any law repealed by that section shall be recognised or given effect to`
  line `under the corresponding provision of the Act or Ordinance now extended.`
